sequenceDiagram
    participant DSP as Data Science Pipelines<br/>(Pipeline Component)
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC/HTTP2<br/>Optional TLS
    participant DB as MySQL/MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP<br/>Optional SSL
    participant UI as DSP UI / Pipeline Client

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Metadata Recording
    DSP->>MLMD: PutExecution (artifacts, events, contexts)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2<br/>Optional mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE metadata records<br/>MySQL protocol<br/>Optional SSL<br/>Username/password auth
    DB-->>MLMD: Confirmation
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutExecutionResponse

    DSP->>MLMD: PutArtifacts (datasets, models, metrics)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE artifact records
    DB-->>MLMD: Confirmation
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutArtifactsResponse

    DSP->>MLMD: PutEvents (artifact-execution links)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT event records
    DB-->>MLMD: Confirmation
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutEventsResponse

    Note over UI,DB: Flow 2: Lineage Query
    UI->>MLMD: GetLineageSubgraph<br/>gRPC/HTTP2<br/>Optional mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT lineage graph data<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL protocol<br/>Optional SSL
    DB-->>MLMD: Query results
    MLMD-->>UI: LineageSubgraph response<br/>gRPC/HTTP2<br/>Optional TLS

    UI->>MLMD: GetArtifactsByContext<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT artifacts by context
    DB-->>MLMD: Query results
    MLMD-->>UI: Artifacts list response
